== 字源 ==
特拉法加廣場的名稱出自[[特拉法加海戰|特拉法加海戰]]，[[拿破崙戰爭|拿破崙戰爭]]中[[英國皇家海軍|英國皇家海軍]]打敗[[法國|法國]]與[[西班牙|西班牙]]的一場戰役，事件發生於西班牙西南部的[[特拉法加角|特拉法加角]]。而特拉法加（Trafalgar）本身則為可以索源於阿拉伯文的西班牙詞語，從''Taraf al-Ghar''（{{lang|ar|طرف الغار}}）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://web.usal.es/~joluin/historiadelalengua/toponimos.htm|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20041215174601/http://web.usal.es/~joluin/historiadelalengua/toponimos.htm|archive-date=15 December 2004|title=2|date=15 December 2004}}</ref><ref>[http://lema.rae.es/drae/?val=algar Entry ''algar''] {{Wayback|url=http://lema.rae.es/drae/?val=algar |date=20200905042600 }}, in [[Diccionario_de_la_lengua_española_de_la_Real_Academia_Española|''DRAE'' dictionary]]</ref><ref name='burton'/> 或 ''Taraf al-Gharb''（{{lang|ar|طرف الغرب}}）演變而來<ref>{{cite web|author=Joseph E. Garreau|url=http://faculty.uml.edu/jgarreau/50.315/Europ1.htm|title=A Cultural Introduction to the Languages of Europe|accessdate=25 March 2019|archive-date=2017-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110075314/http://faculty.uml.edu/jgarreau/50.315/Europ1.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name='burton'>{{cite web|author=[[Richard_Francis_Burton|Richard Burton]]|url=http://www.wollamshram.ca/1001/Vol_9/v9notes.htm#82|title=The Arabian Nights|volume=9|at=footnote 82|access-date=2019-10-17|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227085318/http://www.wollamshram.ca/1001/Vol_9/v9notes.htm#82|dead-url=no}}</ref>，意思為有洞穴的海角或西方的海角。

== 歷史 ==
1950年代的建築工程發掘出上一個[[間冰期|間冰期]]的動物骸骨，包括[[穴獅|穴獅]]、[[犀牛|犀牛]]、[[古菱齒象|古菱齒象]]和[[河馬|河馬]]<ref>{{Cite book|title=On the track of Ice Age mammals|last=Sutcliffe|first=A.J.|publisher=Harvard University Press|year=1985|isbn=978-0674637771|location=https://archive.org/stream/ontrackoficeagem00sutc|pages=139|quote=|via=|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/ontrackoficeagem00sutc}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Franks|first=J.W.|title=Interglacial deposits at Trafalgar Square, London.|journal=The New Phytologist|year=1960|volume=59|issue=2|pages=145–150|jstor=2429192|doi=10.1111/j.1469-8137.1960.tb06212.x}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Interglacial Deposits at Trafalgar Square, London|journal = New Phytologist|volume = 59|issue = 2|pages = 145–152|author=J W Franks|date=9 September 1959|doi=10.1111/j.1469-8137.1960.tb06212.x}}</ref>。

特拉法加廣場所在地於13世紀開始已經具重大意義。於[[愛德華一世|愛德華一世]]在位期間，當地建有[[皇家馬廄|皇家馬廄]]{{sfn|Weinreb et al.|2008|p=934}}。從[[理查二世_(英格兰)|理查二世]]至[[亨利七世_(英格兰)|亨利七世]]年間，馬廄都位處[[河岸街|河岸街]]的西端，直到[[喬治四世|喬治四世]]將之搬遷至[[白金漢宮|白金漢宮]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.royalcollection.org.uk/visit/royalmews/about/the-history-of-the-royal-mews|title=The History of the Royal Mews|publisher=Royal Collection Trust|accessdate=25 November 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125160805/https://www.royalcollection.org.uk/visit/royalmews/about/the-history-of-the-royal-mews|archive-date=2015-11-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 鴿子廣場 ==
